      "source": "Delhi MAGICL 6000i, serial M022W0000396. Network + LIS settings captured from the analyzer System Setup screens (2026-07-24). Noble targets resolved and name-verified against the live catalog on 2026-07-24; the 9 numeric item-ids reused here were verified on the Karnal MAGICL against real eLab Assist HL7 traffic.",
